  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to know the distribution of Helicobacter pylori in stomach
      before subtotal gastrectomy and after subtotal gastrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Endoscopy and biopsy will be performed to investigate the distribution of Helicobacter pylori
      before and after subtotal gastrectomy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
