      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients who are indicated to subtotal gastrectomy due to gastric neoplasm

          2. Aged between 19 to 75 years

          3. Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Previous history of Helicobacter pylori eradication

          2. Previous history of proton pump inhibitor use within 6 months
      </textblock>
